menu "Stock Monitor"

config STOCK_SYMBOL
    string "Ticker symbol"
    default "AAPL"
    help
      The stock ticker to display, e.g. AAPL, MSFT, TSLA, NVDA.

config STOCK_FINNHUB_API_KEY
    string "Finnhub API key"
    default ""
    help
      Free key from https://finnhub.io. Used for quote, fundamentals and
      news. Stored per-developer in your local sdkconfig — do NOT commit a
      real key. Leave empty to disable the Finnhub-backed screens.

config STOCK_WIFI_SSID
    string "WiFi SSID"
    default ""
    help
      2.4GHz network the board joins on boot. (WiFi provisioning is left for
      you to customize; this is a simple Kconfig-driven station connect.)

config STOCK_WIFI_PASSWORD
    string "WiFi password"
    default ""

config STOCK_ROTATE_SECONDS
    int "Screen rotate interval (seconds)"
    default 3
    range 1 60
    help
      How often the bottom area cycles chart -> news -> metrics.

config STOCK_REFRESH_SECONDS
    int "Data refresh interval (seconds)"
    default 30
    range 10 600
    help
      How often data is re-fetched. Keep >= 10s to respect free-tier API
      rate limits; the screen still rotates every ROTATE_SECONDS from cache.

endmenu
